Company Overview of Egencia LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Egencia LLC provides online travel services to businesses worldwide. It offers technology solutions, including online booking; Egencia, a trip navigator for iPad; travel manager tools; reporting; and Egencia Hotel that enables business travelers to access hotels and help them find the right hotel. The company also provides service solutions, such as agent services, VIP executive travel, account management, implementations, groups and meetings, and consulting. It serves business travelers, travel arrangers, travel managers, and CFO and procurement. Egencia LLC was formerly known as Expedia Corporate Travel, Inc. and changed its name to Egencia LLC in July 2008. The company was founded in 2002...
Egencia LLC provides online travel services to businesses worldwide. It offers technology solutions, including online booking; Egencia, a trip navigator for iPad; travel manager tools; reporting; and Egencia Hotel that enables business travelers to access hotels and help them find the right hotel. The company also provides service solutions, such as agent services, VIP executive travel, account management, implementations, groups and meetings, and consulting. It serves business travelers, travel arrangers, travel managers, and CFO and procurement. Egencia LLC was formerly known as Expedia Corporate Travel, Inc. and changed its name to Egencia LLC in July 2008. The company was founded in 2002 and is based in Bellevue, Washington with operations worldwide. Egencia LLC operates as a subsidiary of Expedia Inc.
Detailed Description


